  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Pest Control Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Pest Pro is the modern pest control company. Through prevention, new technology and sustainable solutions, we meet the new demands for healthy environments, for both individuals and businesses.</strong></p><p><strong>Due to growth, we’re looking for experience Pest Control Technicians to join our team. As part of your role, you will be responsible for the below duties:</strong></p><p></p><p>•\tExecute pest service work and carry out inspections and treatments at customer sites</p><p>•\tTo advise clients on pest management’s best practices and problems</p><p>•\tIdentify and solve pest infestation issues with advised time span</p><p>•\tMaintain the provided work equipment in good working condition</p><p>•\tProvide post service work and record service reports, daily work reports and other work-related in a timely manner</p><p></p><p><strong>What we’re looking for:</strong></p><p><strong>Pest Control Technicians</strong></p><p>•\t1-2 Years of working experience in the related field</p><p>•\tPossess good teamwork & strong commitment in work</p><p></p><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><p>•\tBasic Salary $2,000 -$3,000 (OTE $24,000 - $36,000 P.A.)</p><p>•\tCompany welfares & Benefits</p><p>•\tCompany vehicle + phone</p><p>•\tOther incentives</p><p>•\tCommission on upsell opportunities you identify while at client sites</p><p>•\tOpportunity for career progression, training and development</p><p></p><p><strong>If you would like to know more, apply today as we’d love to hear from you!</strong></p>",
